channel.title: How do you add the GE to a 317 server?
channel.description:
[center] :D I know its possible so don't tell me its not, and do not flame on this post! Please just send me a tutorial or post it on here and I'll give ++rep++ :D[/center]
:| As you know I had alot of questions in the past, but right now I switched from a 614 to a 317 because you cant even open a bank in a 614. I will give it some time before they come out with an actual 614 client and server that works thank you! :|
